description:
Martin ,  Java and  the researcher  Nadia  wander  in the wilderness of  Siberian ice , and  now  desperate  to survive .  But  when  all seems lost ,  help arrives , given  by Martin's friend  Strokov . 
In the second part  of the issue ,  a series of murders  in Japan  and in Florida  seem to be related  to the return of  an old friend,  Vincent  Von  Hansen, now  battered and  drunk  after having  disappeared during  an expedition to find  the Fountain of Youth .
name: Viaggio nel futuro

description: Two  scientists ,  Harris and  Shirato ,  were killed  by unknown  assassins ,  behind which  there is  the shadow of  Sergei  Orloff .  The motive  of the crimes  is an extraordinary  discovery that  Shirato  made  ​​on the Japanese island  of   Min.  Martin  Mystere  and  Von  Hansen  go  to Tokyo to  investigate  what has happened .
name: Ritorno dall'aldilà

description: What is the origin of the charm that the Japanese people feel for robots and automation? The answer will be revealed in the epilogue of this adventure in Japan, which sees Mystere and Von Hansen opposed to Sergei Orloff and the Yakuza, the formidable Japanese mafia. Then a new story that will bring Martin to face, after twenty years, with the death of their parents.
name: L'uomo d'acciaio

description: Martin receives a letter from a lawyer of his father, who died along with his mother in a plane crash twenty years earlier. The content is shocking: it tells of some events in which the protagonists are Mark Mystere, the Australian Aborigines and the Men in Black.
name: Incontri ravvicinati

description: Leading scientists are committing suicide because of remorse for ancient crimes, never really committed. Mystère is also struggling with a false memory: the killing of a colleague to take credit for his discoveries. A concoction of Men in Black, which very nearly led him to madness. In the following story Martin ha sto deal with a couple of bizarre beings: a cat and a harpy, from an unknown dimension, and a murderer with a "third eye".
name: La sfera di cristallo

description: Carl “Crusher” Creel is the Absorbing Man. But soon, he shall become something more, for the Hammers of the Serpent have chosen their wielders. Discover Creel’s story and learn how he came to be an instrument of the Serpent.
name: The Worthy: Absorbing Man

description: Martin is involved in a collision with a murderer with a "third eye" which gives him catastrophic powers. Allies of the Detective are an old woman, apparently dead, and a group of "scanners", humans with extraordinary mental abilities. In an attempt to cross the entrance to the parallel dimension from which the murderer would come, Martin and Java come in Mato Grosso, in search of a labyrinth beneath a vertical wall of water.
name: Il terzo occhio

description:
Martin Mystere defeats a fearsome murderer before his telepathic powers to cause a disaster at the Olympic Games in Los Angeles, and then faces a new adventure.

An extraordinary scientific experiment that will test the destructive action of time on the matter, has caused a mutation in a dangerous mosquito. Two professors at MIT are dying as a result of insect bites and Diana herself miraculously survives their attack.
name: La camera del tempo

description: An unpublished manuscript by Giovanni Boccaccio, and the mysterious bonds that link the writer of the fourteenth century to the Etruscans. An ancient device that allows you to fly and the Labyrinth of Porsenna, a secret place that holds a great treasure. These are the ingredients of adventure that leads Martin in Certaldo, Tuscany, the town that was the birthplace of Boccaccio.
name: Decameron!

description: The Magi, the legendary masters of the occult who came to worship Jesus, are still alive, or at least two of them. Melchior and Gaspar are, in fact, risen from the flames and instructed Martin Mystere to find the tomb of Baldassare, the third king. But the Detective has to deal with the Necromancers, the heirs of Herod's henchmen who are willing to do anything to stop him.
name: Il ritorno dei Magi

description: "In the end Balthasar was love and tree…" What's the meaning hidden in the words of this old hymn? Martin is committed to the search of the tomb of the third of the Magi, whose discovery is essential to be able to bring him back to life. The research of the detective then moves from Milan to Lebanon where, to accomplish its mission, he will face many dangers.
name: I Negromanti

description: Martin and Java are once again grappling with the mysteries of Venice. This time they encounter  the fascinating Jewish culture and its legendary golems, creatures that Martin will help because forced, but that ultimately led him to reflect.
name: La casa dalle finestre cieche

description: Collects : X-Men (1991) #74,75

Get it here: the past, present and future of the world's greatest archer - set to star in the upcoming AVENGERS movie! Hawkeye is left blindsided after the events of WIDOWMAKER, with a new vision of the world around him. To move forward with his new life, he must first reexamine how it all began. An all-new era for the Avenging Archer begins here as writer Jim McCann (WIDOWMAKER, Return of the Dapper Men) brings you a Clint Barton you've never seen before! Plus: a classic tale of marksmanship as Hawkeye faces off against Batroc, Oddball and the Taskmaster!
name: TPB

description: Four episodes centered around the theme of the color, and colored with four different editing techniques.
name: Lo spettro della luce

description: Spoleto, Umbria. In the city of the “Festival of Two Worlds”, the Detective of the Impossible and Java are struggling with a modern druid who, referring to ancient Celtic traditions that Italy seems to have forgotten, can dominate a flock of crows, and uses them as deadly weapons against those who come to fight his crazy plans for revenge.
name: I vendicatori alati

description: The zahir, as it was described by writer Jorge Luis Borges, is a fantastic object with the characteristic to remain indelibly imprinted in the minds of those who see it even just once. In this adventure, as Martin discovers, the zahir is also an ancient coin, mysteriously tied to the walls of Bologna, Italy, and capable of driving people insane.
name: Oltre le mura

description: A man called Muley Xeque contacts Martin to propose him the role of advisor in the negotiations about the sale of some special books: those coming from the lost library of Alexandria! Martin pretends to accept, in order to find out about this alleged discovery,and finds himself catapulted into Egypt, among beggars and fake cops.
name: La biblioteca dimenticata

description: The city of Venice sees Martin and Java to deal with a mysterious Marquis, who claims to be Giacomo Casanova and possesses the secret of the great opera sought for centuries by alchemists. A congregation of masked man that threaten Martin and the Marquis seems to confirm the story.
name: Casanova

description: Carbon date your calendars and set the alarm on your Doomsday Clock! Radioactive Man is back in a mega-big book featuring five fantastic tales of irradiated adventure!
name: Matt Groening, Man of Tomorrow  Presents: Radioactive Man

description:
Green Hornet: Blood Ties is a precursor to Kevin Smith's Green Hornet series, and features the original Green Hornet and Kato in action! Ande Parks and Johnny Desjardins tell the exciting story of the last remains of the Italian Crime Family and the Japanese Yakuza.

How did the two-man team of The Green Hornet and Kato bring about the fall of all crime in Century City? Find out here!
name: Blood Ties

description:
Maya Lopez, dubbed Echo by the press, is a young deaf woman capable of replicating any action she sees - including an individual's fighting style.

She once nearly took down Daredevil, believing him to be the one who killed her father. After learning that it was actually Wilson Fisk, her legal guardian, who was responsible, she shot him and left New York in an attempt to discover herself. Now, with her perceptions completely altered, can she make sense of the world? Echo embarks on a Native American vision quest to pick up the pieces of her shattered life.
name: HC
